00:15:05.490 --> 00:15:10.550
I heard many are infected. Stay home. Don't put yourself out there.

00:15:10.550 --> 00:15:13.290
I want to do that, too, but...

00:15:16.830 --> 00:15:19.060
we can't all stay put.

00:15:19.060 --> 00:15:22.340
- What?
- I'm busy right now. I will call you later.

