[Lieutenant Colonel Han Tae Seok]

00:15:29.260 --> 00:15:33.000
Colonel? Can we meet?

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:36.420
What do you mean when? As soon as possible.

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:43.490
You know Park Min Ji was taking a drug, right? Did you take it, too?

00:15:45.300 --> 00:15:49.540
Did Min Ji turn like that because of that drug?

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:54.760
You can't run away now anyway so stay still in here.

00:15:54.760 --> 00:15:58.980
Well, you can consult a lawyer if you want.

00:16:01.820 --> 00:16:05.650
Me, too? But I don't even live here.

00:16:05.650 --> 00:16:08.740
No one can leave, and no one can come in.

00:16:09.470 --> 00:16:12.250
You're a cop. Can't you do something?

00:16:12.250 --> 00:16:14.600
I can't leave, either.

00:16:17.020 --> 00:16:19.470
I heard there's a residents meeting soon. Let's go down together.

00:16:19.470 --> 00:16:25.020
