00:16:25.020 --> 00:16:28.770
Then are you going to stay in here with Oh Joo Hyung?

00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:38.570
Just a moment.

00:16:50.790 --> 00:16:54.130
What now? What, what, what?

00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:03.720
I'm worried about Woo Sang Hee.

00:17:03.720 --> 00:17:07.610
I will release you later. Take a nap.

00:17:07.610 --> 00:17:12.220
What the hell are you doing right now? Why are you doing this to me?

00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:18.520
How about going to the bathroom? The bathroom... Should I just release it in the room?

00:17:24.560 --> 00:17:26.520
Don't spill.

00:17:39.310 --> 00:17:40.820
Are you really not going?

00:17:40.820 --> 00:17:45.290
I really want to go, but you know how sensitive I am.

00:17:45.290 --> 00:17:48.760
