00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:12.780
So Yoon, fighting.

00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:22.430
Hello.

00:18:23.650 --> 00:18:29.630
I heard you arrested the ahjussi across the hallway. Where is he now?

00:18:29.630 --> 00:18:32.000
He's at home,

00:18:32.850 --> 00:18:39.300
due to the lockdown. I handcuffed him so you can tell your husband to go see him for a consultation.

00:18:39.300 --> 00:18:43.020
Is there proof of the murder?

00:18:43.020 --> 00:18:46.530
You should ask him directly about that too.

00:18:46.530 --> 00:18:51.690
But if I were you two, I wouldn't take his case.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:02.380
Sang Hee! Sang Hee, you're out there, right? Sang Hee, please

00:19:02.380 --> 00:19:06.270
talk to me, all right? We live and die together. Hey!

00:19:06.270 --> 00:19:08.410
No.

00:19:08.410 --> 00:19:11.930
Hey, do you think you can live a good life by yourself?

00:19:11.930 --> 00:19:16.600
Everyone will know you as a cheater, and you can't even get out of here because of the lockdown.

00:19:16.600 --> 00:19:20.730
You have no money, and you'll probably get fired from the hospital. The only one who could understand you

00:19:20.730 --> 00:19:23.470
is me, Sang Hee.

00:19:23.470 --> 00:19:27.060
You know me, you know?

00:19:27.060 --> 00:19:31.390
Sang Hee, I'll give you money. Okay?

00:19:32.160 --> 00:19:33.830
Sang Hee!

00:19:34.500 --> 00:19:36.780
How much money would you give me?

00:19:53.170 --> 00:19:57.130
Hello. I'm the wife of attorney Gook Hae Sung in unit 602.

00:19:57.130 --> 00:20:01.670
Please call this number here if you have any legal problems.

00:20:03.390 --> 00:20:05.560
They don't know anything about a drug.

00:20:05.560 --> 00:20:09.940
They got all angry, saying that they don't take steroids.

