00:20:47.190 --> 00:20:50.820
the entire apartment complex will be in cohort quarantine for a week.

00:20:50.820 --> 00:20:55.370
Wait, wait! Wait, Ma'am! I don't even live here. Do I have to be locked up in here?

00:20:55.370 --> 00:20:58.250
Until the management of infected and total inspection is possible,

00:20:58.250 --> 00:21:02.500
- we will compensate for the damages caused by the lockdown.
