We will make sure there are no inconveniences, including meals and other needs.

00:21:06.320 --> 00:21:10.260
Please hang in there with us. If you need anything in addition,

00:21:10.260 --> 00:21:14.110
please discuss among yourselves and let me know. That will be all.

00:21:14.110 --> 00:21:17.970
- Wait, that can't be!
- Wait, no! Wait!

00:21:17.970 --> 00:21:20.890
Geez, Ahjussi!

00:21:20.890 --> 00:21:25.500
I'm sure you're all in shock, but if you're a Seyang Forest Le Ciel resident,

00:21:25.500 --> 00:21:28.680
I believe you will calmly overcome this crisis.

00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:30.670
What do you mean, calm?

00:21:30.670 --> 00:21:34.160
Now, now. I can't hear you if everyone speaks at once.

00:21:34.160 --> 00:21:37.380
I will give you a chance to speak in order.

00:21:37.380 --> 00:21:42.350
Is this because there was an infected person here yesterday? My goodness!

00:21:42.350 --> 00:21:48.120
