00:22:18.690 --> 00:22:23.720
- Since we are all together in this small space, we would all bite, kill and taste each other...
- Gosh, my head hurts.

00:22:23.720 --> 00:22:29.340
To be honest, I don't think there are any more infected people among the residents in our building.

00:22:29.340 --> 00:22:31.950
Everyone here is so sophisticated.

00:22:31.950 --> 00:22:35.810
Fortunately, we have cops here as well.

00:22:35.810 --> 00:22:37.630
Sirs?

00:22:39.080 --> 00:22:42.420
Don't look at me. I will suffocate. You go out.

00:22:48.090 --> 00:22:51.130
Some characteristic behaviors are displayed right before the disease surfaces.

00:22:51.130 --> 00:22:56.720
You feel extreme thirst and your pupils shrink, making your eyes look white.

00:22:56.720 --> 00:23:01.450
When one is alone in an empty space, they knock on walls or display some obsessive behaviors.

00:23:01.450 --> 00:23:04.670
If possible, get together with more than two people

00:23:04.670 --> 00:23:07.790
and leave a door open while you're together.

00:23:07.790 --> 00:23:11.070
If you notice that you are behaving suspiciously, ask for help from those around you right away.

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:13.540
But I live alone! How could I be with two or more?

00:23:13.540 --> 00:23:15.460
It's for a week.

00:23:17.150 --> 00:23:21.520
We only have to hang on for a week.

00:23:23.290 --> 00:23:26.230
[Exit]

00:23:47.370 --> 00:23:52.930
You wanted to lock this place down while the children were at school. I noticed you stopped the cars from coming home.

00:23:52.930 --> 00:23:55.900
You wanted a lockdown without children, right?

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:58.820
That would look better.

00:23:58.820 --> 00:24:02.500
There is a child who didn't go to school. Let her leave.

00:24:02.500 --> 00:24:05.610
You could do that much, can't you?

00:24:05.610 --> 00:24:08.690
Park Seo Yoon, we are testing her parents.

00:24:08.690 --> 00:24:11.280
Both of them are highly likely to be infected.

00:24:12.990 --> 00:24:18.330
- Are you sure?
- Delivery work is tough. They probably took it as a stimulant.

00:24:18.330 --> 00:24:23.490
I'm sure they're calling the child and saying, "I love you, I miss you."

00:24:23.490 --> 00:24:29.210
That's all useless. No one knows how drastically people could change when push comes to shove.

00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:36.130
Colonel, talk about your pessimistic view of family with your blind date.

00:24:36.130 --> 00:24:38.080
What do you want me to do?

00:24:40.100 --> 00:24:44.320
I'm saying it's better for Seo Yoon to stay in here with a good guardian.

00:24:44.320 --> 00:24:46.330
On the outside...

00:24:49.660 --> 00:24:52.250
you just don't know how things could change.

00:24:55.660 --> 00:24:57.820
Ahjussi Cop,

00:24:57.820 --> 00:25:03.310
the wall outside... It looks like I could climb over it if I tried.

00:25:03.310 --> 00:25:07.260
Would I get punished if I climbed over it?

00:25:07.260 --> 00:25:11.880
More than that, I'm sure the reporters outside would be delighted.

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:15.330
You might even make it to the evening news.

00:25:15.330 --> 00:25:20.510
How about food? Are we eating on our own?

00:25:20.510 --> 00:25:25.990
We'll pass out lunch boxes starting tomorrow morning. You have something to eat tonight, right?

00:25:25.990 --> 00:25:28.680
But where are the apartment management people?

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:33.060
The apartment building was put in lockdown at 9:30 a.m., but no one had come into work by then.

00:25:33.060 --> 00:25:37.360
The night shift staff went to a meeting in another building. This doesn't make any sense at all.

00:25:37.360 --> 00:25:43.120
What, what, what? So other buildings are meeting without us?

00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:45.990
They're scared because the first infected person was our building.

00:25:45.990 --> 00:25:49.130
They have abandoned their duty.

00:25:49.130 --> 00:25:53.110
Then no one from the management office is in this building?

00:25:57.540 --> 00:26:02.900
Yes, no one is here. Something we shouldn't keep quiet about has happened.

00:26:02.900 --> 00:26:05.060
There's someone outside.

00:26:08.930 --> 00:26:14.500
I lived in the States with my husband, but we returned to Korea because we fell in love with Korea's disease prevention.

00:26:14.500 --> 00:26:19.900
Excuse me, Building Representative. The management office staff is standing outside.

00:26:23.530 --> 00:26:26.620
It's not just this incident. There is a lot of corruption in this apartment building.

00:26:26.620 --> 00:26:30.450
Do you know that they fixed the elevator in secret because it failed the installation inspection?

00:26:30.450 --> 00:26:36.820
They collect recyclables only once a week, and they're spending money to maintain roadside trees inside the complex. Did you know that?

00:26:36.820 --> 00:26:42.090
If you trust and follow me, I will represent all the residents

00:26:42.090 --> 00:26:47.390
and resolve all the irregularities within this apartment complex.

00:26:48.170 --> 00:26:51.020
Please allow the renters to use the gym as well.

00:26:52.010 --> 00:26:57.120
My husband went to a seminar in Kentucky in the US.

00:26:57.120 --> 00:27:02.600
I'm sure some of you are wondering about the church service due to the lockdown.

00:27:02.600 --> 00:27:09.530
Hallelujah. God is always by your side.

00:27:09.530 --> 00:27:14.480
All the believers can come to me.

00:27:16.100 --> 00:27:22.180
If anyone needs a damage compensation estimate due to the lockdown or needs any legal advice, please talk to me.

00:27:22.180 --> 00:27:25.330
We'll serve you with quality legal representation.

00:27:25.330 --> 00:27:27.730
Please come to unit 602.

00:27:27.730 --> 00:27:31.200
- Let's go.
- Hurry up and come.

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:33.460
Gosh, I'm so annoyed.

00:27:39.770 --> 00:27:43.600
I heard you're some kind of police, too.

00:27:43.600 --> 00:27:46.960
You should cooperate with keeping the order inside the apartment building.

00:27:46.960 --> 00:27:51.730
I work in a different field. I only learned to suppress terrorists.

00:27:51.730 --> 00:27:54.690
Please talk to me if you need any cooperation.

00:28:04.200 --> 00:28:07.890
Am I getting paid more? I don't think so.

00:28:07.890 --> 00:28:11.290
However, I'm sure it will help me with my promotion.

00:28:11.290 --> 00:28:15.360
Gosh, I had no idea when I came in here. I want to go home and make deliveries, too.

00:28:15.360 --> 00:28:18.950
What is this about?

00:28:18.950 --> 00:28:22.390
You have to tell me so I can talk, too.

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:29.000
- Why lock the door...
- Let me ask you one thing. Are you close with this person?
[Kim Joo Heon]

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:33.720
Joo Heon? No, we work alternate days so I haven't even seen him that often.

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:38.190
And he stopped coming into work a few days ago so I came in every day.

00:28:45.760 --> 00:28:50.210
You drink so much water. Do you keep getting thirsty?

00:28:50.210 --> 00:28:52.160
I've always drunk a lot of water.

00:28:52.160 --> 00:28:56.500
Can you open this? Oh, I'm from the Special Operations Unit.

00:28:56.500 --> 00:28:59.030
Sure. Okay.

00:29:00.600 --> 00:29:02.310
Go ahead and look.

00:29:07.110 --> 00:29:11.040
One of your colleagues sold some drugs here.

00:29:11.040 --> 00:29:16.010
The authorities believe that the drug is causing that Madman Rabies.

00:29:16.010 --> 00:29:18.410
You're aware of the symptoms, right?

00:29:18.410 --> 00:29:22.340
Extreme thirst. Hallucinations.

00:29:27.230 --> 00:29:29.870
Be straight with us. Did you take the drug?

00:29:29.870 --> 00:29:34.570
No. I didn't take anything besides supplements.

00:29:34.570 --> 00:29:36.900
You know who took them, right?

00:29:36.900 --> 00:29:41.130
If you don't tell us now, you could be charged with selling drugs.

00:29:41.130 --> 00:29:44.350
Gosh, I really don't know.

00:29:44.350 --> 00:29:47.700
Hiding the truth isn't going to get you anywhere.

00:29:47.700 --> 00:29:50.790
The entire apartment complex is in lockdown because of you. Do you know that?

00:29:50.790 --> 00:29:53.120
I said no!

00:29:56.630 --> 00:30:00.330
I mean, you two keep cornering me

00:30:00.330 --> 00:30:06.130
as the bad guy. I really didn't take a drug like that.

00:30:23.320 --> 00:30:26.880
We have a bunch of cleaning appointments to catch up this week.

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:29.810
Could there be any way we could take care of this?

00:30:29.810 --> 00:30:34.130
Sir, I came in here unexpectedly and can't leave.

00:30:34.130 --> 00:30:36.450
They say they'll compensate for all the damages incurred.

00:30:36.450 --> 00:30:39.650
Let's just wait.

00:30:39.650 --> 00:30:42.690
Do you two have a place to sleep?

00:30:42.690 --> 00:30:44.770
No, we don't.

00:30:44.770 --> 00:30:47.680
We have a child at home.

00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:48.870
How old is your child?

00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:50.900
He is seventeen years old.

00:30:50.900 --> 00:30:52.930
Seventeen.

00:30:53.800 --> 00:30:58.040
I'll check in with them to see if they'll allow you to sleep in the space you were cleaning.

00:30:58.040 --> 00:31:00.920
Is he with you?

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:04.320
Oh, he works for us.

00:31:04.320 --> 00:31:07.070
Can you tell me your name, please?

00:31:07.070 --> 00:31:08.690
My name is Andrew.

00:31:08.690 --> 00:31:10.380
What?

00:31:10.380 --> 00:31:13.090
Hey, can you wait a second?

00:31:18.060 --> 00:31:22.210
He is a little autistic, but he is a kind boy.

00:31:22.210 --> 00:31:25.400
He hurt his face when he was young so he has a lot of scars.

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:27.790
He was always home, unable to go out,

00:31:27.790 --> 00:31:31.550
but nowadays, people don't mind others wearing masks.

00:31:31.550 --> 00:31:33.890
He mustered up the courage to start working.

00:31:33.890 --> 00:31:35.760
Understood.

00:31:35.760 --> 00:31:39.280
- You all have your IDs, right?
- Yes.

00:31:39.280 --> 00:31:43.560
Can I see them? They need a list of people who are in the building.

00:31:50.410 --> 00:31:52.810
[Ahn Guk Jin]

00:31:52.810 --> 00:31:55.210
Oh, I scratched it out.

00:31:57.580 --> 00:32:00.490
Ahn Guk Jin.

00:32:00.490 --> 00:32:04.300
Then why did you say your name was Andrew?

00:32:06.310 --> 00:32:08.860
Because I would love to have some superpowers.

00:32:08.860 --> 00:32:12.290
There was a drama like that a long time ago.

00:32:12.290 --> 00:32:14.650
[Ahn Guk Jin]

00:32:20.940 --> 00:32:24.350
Who were you talking to that you're hanging up so quickly?

00:32:24.350 --> 00:32:27.300
I was talking to a friend.

00:32:27.300 --> 00:32:28.320
Should we tie him up?

00:32:28.320 --> 00:32:30.040
We don't know just yet.

00:32:30.040 --> 00:32:33.720
We won't tie you up so stay in here, okay?

00:32:33.720 --> 00:32:37.280
Kim Seung Beom, if I catch you outside this office,

00:32:37.280 --> 00:32:39.760
I'll just assume you're infected.

00:32:39.760 --> 00:32:41.680
Let's see...

00:32:44.850 --> 00:32:47.260
if you can hold off drinking water until the morning.

00:32:54.150 --> 00:32:58.450
[Do not enter, risk of infection!]

00:32:58.450 --> 00:33:02.760
You'll get thirsty if you stay awake so don't look at your cell phone and go to sleep.

00:33:05.050 --> 00:33:07.640
[Unit 601, Unit 1202, Unit 602]

00:33:07.640 --> 00:33:09.780
[Unit 601- Park Min Ji, Unit 1202 - Seon Woo Chang, Unit 602 - Sin So Yoon]

00:33:12.750 --> 00:33:17.500
Hey, good thing they didn't allow renters to use the gym.

00:33:17.500 --> 00:33:19.930
We have fewer suspected infected people.

00:33:20.900 --> 00:33:25.260
You are really a police officer.

00:33:26.990 --> 00:33:28.660
Of course.

00:33:28.660 --> 00:33:33.280
I went to the gym, but other than that, I was always home.
[1501 | The penthouse]

00:33:33.280 --> 00:33:36.800
I won't leave here until the lockdown is lifted so don't worry about me─

00:33:36.800 --> 00:33:39.230
I'm not here about that. It's something else.

00:33:39.230 --> 00:33:43.050
I need something for the people downstairs.

00:33:43.050 --> 00:33:45.250
Blankets.

00:33:45.250 --> 00:33:48.030
You have army blankets, right?

00:33:51.770 --> 00:33:55.830
I can bring you a T-shirt tomorrow.

00:34:15.040 --> 00:34:16.890
Thank you.

00:34:19.930 --> 00:34:25.480
[Article 1003 (The spouse's order of inheritance)]

00:34:39.980 --> 00:34:42.320
You remember that I live downstairs, right?

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:46.660
If you make noises on purpose, I won't stay put.

00:34:48.420 --> 00:34:50.360
If you don't stay put, what will you do then?

00:34:50.360 --> 00:34:52.660
Ahjussi.

00:34:52.660 --> 00:34:55.180
No one will say anything if I say you died while running away.

00:34:55.180 --> 00:34:57.040
There are tons of people who would say something.

00:34:57.040 --> 00:35:00.340
This is also illegal confinement.

00:35:00.340 --> 00:35:04.100
Moreover, I didn't see your name on the gym entry log.

00:35:04.100 --> 00:35:06.170
Don't you usually exercise?

00:35:06.170 --> 00:35:08.890
Breathing exercises. I also go out to golf courses sometimes.

00:35:08.890 --> 00:35:12.400
My wife used to go to that gym.

00:35:13.930 --> 00:35:18.960
Did madness rabies start spreading at the gym?

00:35:18.960 --> 00:35:21.910
Stop thinking too much unnecessarily.

00:35:21.910 --> 00:35:25.140
If you have time to do that, feel remorse for the murder you committed.

00:35:25.140 --> 00:35:27.830
If you're human, at least.

00:35:32.780 --> 00:35:38.500
Woo Sang Hee, I prepared some change of clothes and a place for you to sleep on the fifth floor so let's go down together.

00:35:38.500 --> 00:35:40.960
I'll just stay here.

00:35:40.960 --> 00:35:45.120
I testified falsely because I was so angry.

00:35:45.120 --> 00:35:49.100
Actually, I never saw nor heard anything that day.

00:35:49.100 --> 00:35:50.720
I'm sorry, Detective.

00:35:50.720 --> 00:35:53.460
Sang Hee fell for your enticing words,

00:35:53.460 --> 00:35:57.300
and thought I really did do something terrible.

00:35:58.260 --> 00:36:03.220
I explained to her that Min Ji's death was accidental.

00:36:24.490 --> 00:36:26.460
[Lieutenant Colonel Han Tae Seok]

00:36:31.060 --> 00:36:34.410
- What?
- Unit 302 is broadcasting what's going on inside the building.

00:36:34.410 --> 00:36:39.200
Stop him right now! If not, I'll shut off both the TV and the internet.

00:36:55.320 --> 00:36:59.870
Hey. Hey, get up for a moment.

00:36:59.870 --> 00:37:02.000
Why?

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:07.630
Did you meet the infected person yesterday?

00:37:07.630 --> 00:37:10.170
Did you just find that out?

00:37:10.980 --> 00:37:13.300
Did you get a scratch?

00:37:13.300 --> 00:37:15.680
No, it's not like that.

00:37:15.680 --> 00:37:18.120
What do you mean, no?

00:37:18.120 --> 00:37:21.370
Aigoo. Why are you doing this?

00:37:21.370 --> 00:37:24.250
I told you I didn't.

00:37:24.250 --> 00:37:28.760
My gosh. You never even bought me any medicine. What in the world...

00:37:29.880 --> 00:37:34.440
Aigoo. This is nothing. Are you lying down over this?

00:37:34.440 --> 00:37:37.430
Drink a glass of soju. It won't hurt at all if you drink.

00:37:37.430 --> 00:37:39.340
Aigoo.

00:37:44.310 --> 00:37:46.820
- Who is it?
- Is your son home?

00:37:46.820 --> 00:37:48.780
I thought he left earlier.

00:37:48.780 --> 00:37:50.240
Do you know where he went?

00:37:50.240 --> 00:37:54.570
I'm sure he's in the building somewhere. Anyway, he's not home.

00:37:56.900 --> 00:37:57.870
I think I know where he is.

00:37:57.870 --> 00:38:01.930
I clearly told you, I won't talk about stocks at all today.

00:38:01.930 --> 00:38:05.180
I have some content today that's not made up at all. Aigoo, Kiro.

00:38:05.180 --> 00:38:09.120
It's good to see you. Our generous Kiro, good to see you.

00:38:09.120 --> 00:38:14.020
Now, everyone. Where is this?

00:38:14.970 --> 00:38:19.500
This is where the first infected was discovered.

00:38:19.500 --> 00:38:25.310
I heard the family still lives here. I'm about to meet and talk to him.

00:38:26.760 --> 00:38:30.380
Should I ring the bell? Well?

00:38:30.380 --> 00:38:32.870
Should I? Or not?

00:38:32.870 --> 00:38:36.380
Should I? Or not?

00:38:36.380 --> 00:38:40.510
Should I? Or not? Should I? Or not?

00:38:40.510 --> 00:38:43.350
Should I beat him up or not?

00:38:43.350 --> 00:38:46.530
Should I hit him? Or not?

00:38:46.530 --> 00:38:49.560
It's going to explode! Explode!

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:53.800
I'm turning this off. Wash up and go to sleep.

00:38:53.800 --> 00:38:56.900
- Bangjong?
- What's this?

00:38:56.900 --> 00:38:58.210
Thank you.

00:38:58.210 --> 00:38:59.930
Is he supposed to be thankful?

00:38:59.930 --> 00:39:04.800
- I got 500,000 won ($500)!
- Crazy...

00:39:06.750 --> 00:39:08.330
- Aish!
- Why did you do that?

00:39:08.330 --> 00:39:10.230
Ahjussi, come over here!

00:39:13.820 --> 00:39:16.740
Gosh, what a long day.

00:39:16.740 --> 00:39:18.720
I know.

00:39:18.720 --> 00:39:21.180
What happened to the dermatologist clinic manager upstairs?

00:39:21.180 --> 00:39:24.660
She fell for Oh Joo Hyung. She says she wants to stay there.

00:39:25.640 --> 00:39:27.580
Hey, should I try to convince her again?

00:39:27.580 --> 00:39:31.090
It's okay. She's an adult. She can take care of herself.

00:39:31.090 --> 00:39:33.720
Could Oh Joo Hyung do something stupid at a time like this?

00:39:33.720 --> 00:39:37.900
Let's just check on her and see if she's okay. I'm exhausted.

00:39:37.900 --> 00:39:42.570
Let's do that. But the sleeping arrangement...

00:39:43.210 --> 00:39:45.180
Where should we...

00:39:47.900 --> 00:39:50.090
Where do I sleep?

00:40:00.020 --> 00:40:02.490
♫ When... ♫

00:40:02.490 --> 00:40:06.000
♫ When did it start to go wrong? ♫

00:40:08.760 --> 00:40:14.760
♫ Where, where did it all go wrong? ♫

00:40:16.230 --> 00:40:21.790
♫ Since when, when did we hurt each other? ♫

00:40:21.790 --> 00:40:26.330
Hey, smile. Smile. One, two.

00:40:27.980 --> 00:40:29.900
What are you doing?

00:40:29.900 --> 00:40:32.710
My wife says to take pictures and send them to her.

00:40:32.710 --> 00:40:36.190
She's asking if I went fishing. Why wouldn't she believe me?

00:40:36.190 --> 00:40:38.250
I can't believe it, either.

00:40:38.250 --> 00:40:39.810
What?

00:40:39.810 --> 00:40:42.640
That I'm here like this with you.

00:40:43.690 --> 00:40:46.920
Gosh, we had good vibes today.

00:40:47.730 --> 00:40:49.610
There.

00:40:51.510 --> 00:40:53.500
We just have to endure a few days.

00:40:53.500 --> 00:40:56.320
Just think that you're vacationing at a villa or something. Okay?

00:40:56.320 --> 00:40:58.000
Okay.

00:41:11.760 --> 00:41:13.820
Are you praying?

00:41:14.670 --> 00:41:17.080
I changed the prayer today.

00:41:17.080 --> 00:41:21.070
I prayed that the lockdown will lift when we wake up tomorrow.

00:41:21.070 --> 00:41:24.770
Okay. I'll pray, too.

00:41:24.770 --> 00:41:27.310
- Good night.
- Good night.

00:41:27.310 --> 00:41:29.620
Sleep tight, Unni.

00:41:29.620 --> 00:41:31.620
Let's sleep now.

00:41:34.940 --> 00:41:36.710
Yi Hyun.

00:41:37.770 --> 00:41:39.030
What?

00:41:39.030 --> 00:41:41.310
I have a bad back.

00:41:44.410 --> 00:41:46.300
All of a sudden?

00:41:49.830 --> 00:41:54.690
- Geez. Sleep on the couch then.
- Thanks.

00:41:58.940 --> 00:42:00.330
This is mine. Take this.

00:42:00.330 --> 00:42:02.870
Okay. Thanks.

00:42:05.170 --> 00:42:08.570
I met the wrong acupuncturist.

00:42:22.790 --> 00:42:27.290
♫ It was destiny ♫

00:42:28.150 --> 00:42:31.880
[Madam Kim Bok Nam: You must be worried a lot, too. Sorry, I keep calling. Congratulations on getting married...]

00:42:31.880 --> 00:42:39.740
[Everything will be fine. Don't worry and stay healthy. Don't become like me. Be happy.]

00:42:45.900 --> 00:42:51.570
♫ When, when did it start to go wrong? ♫

00:42:51.570 --> 00:42:55.490
[You have to be happy, too, Mom]

00:42:57.150 --> 00:42:59.910
♫ Where did we all go wrong? ♫

00:42:59.910 --> 00:43:02.430
[We'll take care of the viral pneumonia treatment.]

00:43:04.390 --> 00:43:09.830
[Team Leader Han Tae Seok assaults chairman, the shadow of A-Team Therapeutics]

00:43:09.830 --> 00:43:14.010
Hyung, I know you're not sleeping.

00:43:15.320 --> 00:43:19.810
- What?
- Do you know Han Tae Seok's assault case?

00:43:19.810 --> 00:43:21.610
What happened to the pharmaceutical chairman?

00:43:21.610 --> 00:43:23.740
What are you talking about?

00:43:23.740 --> 00:43:27.120
If it was assault, it means the guy didn't die.

00:43:28.920 --> 00:43:31.800
I just wonder what he's been up to since then.

